Products.name: Aspirin
Products.description: Aspirin is a common pain reliever and fever reducer.

Products.name: Ibuprofen
Products.description: Ibuprofen is a nonsteroidal anti-inflammatory drug (NSAID) used to relieve pain and reduce fever.

Products.name: Acetaminophen
Products.description: Acetaminophen is a pain reliever and fever reducer that is available over-the-counter.

Products.name: Naproxen
Products.description: Naproxen is an NSAID used to relieve pain, reduce fever, and reduce inflammation.

Products.name: Loratadine
Products.description: Loratadine is an antihistamine used to relieve allergy symptoms, such as runny nose, sneezing, and itchy eyes.

Products.name: Diphenhydramine
Products.description: Diphenhydramine is an antihistamine used to relieve allergy symptoms, such as runny nose, sneezing, and itchy eyes, as well as to treat motion sickness and insomnia.

Products.name: Pseudoephedrine
Products.description: Pseudoephedrine is a decongestant used to relieve nasal congestion caused by allergies, colds, or the flu.

Products.name: Dextromethorphan
Products.description: Dextromethorphan is a cough suppressant used to relieve coughing caused by colds or the flu.

Products.name: Guaifenesin
Products.description: Guaifenesin is an expectorant used to relieve chest congestion caused by colds or the flu.
